{"tid":701012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過望住張相覺得好陌生？","createTime":"2018-06-13T20:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T07:32:48.000Z","uid":13909,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b84bd88d7704aa21a1dbc778451b1afdccdf52e3","tid":701012,"uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T20:24:34.000Z","msg":"或者咁講啦 正常睇返以前嘅相會即刻諗返起果段回憶<br />\n但睇返同前女啲相係唔會即刻有回憶彈出黎<br />\n望住佢個樣覺得好陌生 好似完全唔識咁<br />\n就好似睇緊一張random嘅ig相<br />\n明明一齊過拖過攬過嘴過見過好撚多次<br />\n講緊上一次見面都係二月嘅事<br />\n有無人有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申記性好好 記其他野都記得好清楚"},{"pid":"b7060e7429342e8f07653fed0550eb7a5f1c401a","tid":701012,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T20:53:34.000Z","msg":"你有無愛過你ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4190a11748ce96dca745bf2f3debf3c341fc98fb","tid":701012,"uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b7060e7429342e8f07653fed0550eb7a5f1c401a","tid":701012,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T20:53:34.000Z","msg":"你有無愛過你ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T21:01:52.000Z","msg":"屌梗係有啦 散撚左就黎成年到依家都仲未放得低嗮<br />\n<br />\n但好奇怪 頭先見到你呢句我諗返以前d嘢 就好似睇緊第三者拍拖咁 完全唔覺得係自己黎<br />\nEven睇返d合照 連相入面嘅自己都覺得好陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其他相又唔會"},{"pid":"4c6b704465f253ac889356e10afb4c7eaba21721","tid":701012,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T22:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2c64f77deba26f83511b5f11c401e9a8ff15d7a","tid":701012,"uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c6b704465f253ac889356e10afb4c7eaba21721","tid":701012,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T22:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T22:41:28.000Z","msg":"咩病<img src=\"/a